#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 
$ACTION
Case ACTION
   When "OUVRE"       : Gosub OUVRE
   When "DEBUT"       : Gosub DEBUT
Endcase
Return

$OUVRE
Gosub OUVRE_OUT From ESPASDETAV

#Manage Localisations
Call MANAGE_LOCALISATION("ESSPASDETV") From DIVPAYE

Return

$DEBUT
Gosub DEBUT_OUT From ESPASDETAV

#Manage localisations
Call HIDE_ACTIVITYFIELDS From WESSPASDETVHIDE
Call SHOW_LEGACTCALLS From WESSPASDETVSHOW



Return




